                <note rend="inline" type="source">845.00/4–2845; Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Acting Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">San Francisco</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1945-04-28">April 28,
                            1945</date>.<lb/>[Received April 28—9:43 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>10. I had a discussion with Eden this morning relative to the general Indian
                    problem. He thoroughly understands our position. While he made no commitment I
                    feel that I made some headway with him. You will naturally wish to advise
                    Phillips of this.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Stetttinius</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
